### --- Prerequisites: Create a drone with some flight hours ---

### Create Drone for maintenance tests
POST http://localhost:3000/api/drones
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "serialNumber": "SKY-MT01-TE5T",
  "model": "MATRICE_300"
}

### --- Maintenance CRUD ---

### Create Maintenance Log
POST http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "type": "ROUTINE_CHECK",
  "technicianName": "Alex Smith",
  "notes": "Regular 90-day inspection completed",
  "datePerformed": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "flightHoursAtMaintenance": 0
}

### List Maintenance Logs (paginated)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs?page=1&limit=10

### List Maintenance Logs (filtered by droneId)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs?droneId={{droneId}}

### List Maintenance Logs (filtered by type)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs?type=ROUTINE_CHECK

### Get Maintenance Log by ID
GET http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs/{{maintenanceId}}

### Complete Maintenance (drone → AVAILABLE)
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs/{{maintenanceId}}/complete

### --- Validation Error Cases ---

### Invalid: Drone IN_MISSION (should fail 422)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "type": "BATTERY_REPLACEMENT",
  "technicianName": "Tech",
  "datePerformed": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "flightHoursAtMaintenance": 25
}

### Invalid: Flight hours mismatch (should fail 422)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "droneId": "{{droneId}}",
  "type": "MOTOR_REPAIR",
  "technicianName": "Tech",
  "datePerformed": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "flightHoursAtMaintenance": 999
}

### Invalid: Missing required fields (should fail 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### Invalid: Non-existent drone (should fail 404)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/maintenance-logs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "droneId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "type": "ROUTINE_CHECK",
  "technicianName": "Tech",
  "datePerformed": "2026-04-01T10:00:00Z",
  "flightHoursAtMaintenance": 0
}
